# PSOTS Telegram Bot - Cloudflare Workers Edition
#
# No .env file needed for Cloudflare Workers!
# Bot token is stored as a "wrangler secret" instead.
#
# To set up:
# 1. Run: wrangler secret put BOT_TOKEN
# 2. Paste your bot token when prompted
# 3. Deploy with: wrangler deploy
#
# Admin ID is hardcoded in src/index.js (line ~227)
# Change it there if needed.

# Reference (DO NOT USE IN PRODUCTION):
# BOT_TOKEN = 8526973206:AAEJnvI4_bkJCDE-7q94E-HZl-YLabtQdcI
# ADMIN_ID = 989358143
